ndproc
    --list-sources <rules>
    --disable-rule <comma,separated,numbers,list>
    --sqweeze-blame|--dedup-blame # make blame as small as possible (get rid of intermediate data)
    tests -h -V, --dump-rules, noargs and so on for all modules
    PATH DEFINITION to all mods docs
    'optional' opt to mods opts %)
    validate_rules method for all modules

App::NDTools::NDTool
    --ifmt --ofmt

App::NDTools::NDProc::Module
    complete rule using defaults if not all vital opts provided
    also - non default opts only when dump rules

App::NDTools::NDProc::Module::Insert
    --method append|override|prepend|shift # define a way to add items to arrays (override by default)

App::NDTools::NDProc::Module::Merge
    --match <path> # (combined with path) -- to implement fair pairwise merge (filter like "defined" used)
    --structure # as --source alternative (JSON in args, raw structure in rule)
    make per-merge path opt to be able as list

App::NDTools::NDProc::Module::Copy
    --path --to --move

